Zend_Service_Amazon_Ses

Incubator for development of a new Zend Framework Simple Email Services component.

Usage:

SendEmail:
========================
$sendEmail = new Zend_Service_Amazon_Ses_SendEmail(
    'awskey', 'aws-secret-key'
);

$sendEmail->addTo('to-address@domain.tld', 'Some User')
          ->setSource('from-email@example.com')
          ->setSubject('This is a message')
          ->setBody('Boom Boom Boom!!!')
          ->request();



SendRawEmail:
========================
$sendRawEmail = new Zend_Service_Amazon_Ses_SendEmail(
    'awskey', 'aws-secret-key'
);

$sendRawEmail->setRawEmail('...full email string with headers...')
             ->request();